{"tid":1641933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(推上熱門) 和理非進場之18區和理搭!!","createTime":"2019-10-09T13:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T14:31:24.000Z","uid":311711,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4ccbc41424f6dcb0e289cfb87e395b357b8491","tid":1641933,"uid":311711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"心水清既巴絲都知林鄭推左緊急法之後<br />\n黨鐵日日封鐵自製恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n壞唔壞都好<br />\n出口唔開 閘機唔開 增值機唔開<br />\n8點一到有乘客都照落閘<br />\n林鄭已經冇哂底牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉埋黨鐵玩宵禁仲搏民意反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗諗下有個idea<br />\n不如搞個和理非之18區和理搭!<br />\n和理非全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朝早放工係黨鐵站出面舉牌<br />\n話阻到大家唔好意思(呢個位睇大家睇法)<br />\n教市民除左鐵仲有咩巴士小巴可以坐<br />\nUpdate最新交通消息<br />\n仲可以派巴士路綫圖<br />\n大家自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得6月稅局「對唔住，阻到你，真係好對唔住」<br />\n當時道歉Feedback並唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住我地有二百萬民意基礎<br />\n絕不勢弱言輕 絕不虛作無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人 反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd8a8cf146bd8e9c9139809b3f1132317f0b792","tid":1641933,"uid":133954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁幫手推10"},{"pid":"8ccfc64e28f9a9007c012e92977f39a3703fb008","tid":1641933,"uid":133954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"依家個個都塞鐵8點落閘好應該教下大家巴士既美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2ab881c29ca9ade3ac4e89a93799ce8fdd8412","tid":1641933,"uid":133954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"何況連儂牆功用咁細<br />\n呢個係接觸廣大街坊既好機會"},{"pid":"f128db9817eb3311ac11d3b7f6efe316b1817cb3","tid":1641933,"uid":133954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"全能既連登仔有冇興趣一齊做"},{"pid":"4057b2321a3f33a279717a8dd7c161d16f09a7ee","tid":1641933,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"唔係喎，係黨鐵自己唔俾人搭喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05e567463fd5d13176bb639c567e205d9ca8194","tid":1641933,"uid":133954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4057b2321a3f33a279717a8dd7c161d16f09a7ee","tid":1641933,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"唔係喎，係黨鐵自己唔俾人搭喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:48:25.000Z","msg":"我地幫人搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2088d1af6afe70582046d4cb0397007a1c6549","tid":1641933,"uid":313283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"封黨鐵系政府錯，系政治推波技倆，仲幫佢道歉咪食死貓食到飽？"},{"pid":"8693b459fae224ef6d3f3df8d5479355cf5f59b7","tid":1641933,"uid":133954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"我都覺得唔駛 sorry <br />\n賴落去政府度再幫人搭車"},{"pid":"391be969b37e513a0030a13da57c695c21bdfc79","tid":1641933,"uid":3